x4freetext: MP tandem.
The use of deformation-dependent optical-model
transmission coefficients in statistical-model
calculations at very high angular momenta is consi-
dered. Average gamma-multiplicity.

Fe-54 target was used.

around 0.degr., from reaction, was made with the
Rochester Recoil Mass Spectrometer (see REL-REF).
